18:05.585 --> 18:09.187
<i> ¶ I bless the rains down</i>
<i> in a...</i>

18:09.189 --> 18:10.021
(GASPS) Damn it!

18:10.023 --> 18:14.959
<i> ¶ Gonna take more than that</i>
<i> to make me leave this pla...</i>

18:15.361 --> 18:16.327
Gah! Come on!

18:16.329 --> 18:20.431
<i> ¶ I hate the rains</i>
<i> down in Jenkintown ¶</i>

18:20.433 --> 18:22.233
ADULT ADAM:
<i> While Erica's dreams</i>
<i> broke down,</i>

18:22.235 --> 18:25.636
<i> me and Pops were ready</i>
<i> to build Barry back up.</i>

18:25.638 --> 18:26.871
Hi.

18:27.774 --> 18:28.072
Hey.

18:28.074 --> 18:30.908
So, me and Pops
are starting our Batman movie,

18:30.910 --> 18:33.511
but we couldn't decide
which Batman was better,

18:33.513 --> 18:35.446
so we're gonna have both.
Sounds fun.

18:35.448 --> 18:38.716
Actually, we thought you could
have some fun with us.

18:38.718 --> 18:42.520
Really?
I mean, we got
the superheroes,

18:42.522 --> 18:43.654
but no one for us to fight.

18:43.656 --> 18:46.824
I don't know.
I didn't really like
being the Joker.

18:46.826 --> 18:49.227
I think this time you will.

18:49.529 --> 18:51.229
Follow us.

18:52.966 --> 18:56.300
No way!
A BMX Batman movie?

18:56.302 --> 18:58.402
Look, we never meant
to leave you out,

18:58.404 --> 19:02.840
and now that you're here,
I say we turn
the dynamic duo

19:02.842 --> 19:05.510
