<i> ¶ There's nothing that</i>
<i> a hundred men or more</i>
<i> could ever do ¶</i>

19:15.121 --> 19:17.989
How's it going?
It's going great.

19:17.991 --> 19:20.491
Listen, I realized
you were right about me,

19:20.493 --> 19:24.428
screaming at you
all these years
about finishing college,

19:24.430 --> 19:25.663
and I didn't even
see it through.

19:25.665 --> 19:28.799
