make me go home
and apply to new schools?

19:28.801 --> 19:30.201
I'd like to, but I can't,

19:30.203 --> 19:32.236
not after lying to you
all these years.

19:32.238 --> 19:34.939
So that's it?
Tell me I'm a moron!

19:34.941 --> 19:36.941
Tell me not to
give up on myself!

19:36.943 --> 19:38.209
Tell me to apply
to new schools

19:38.211 --> 19:40.077
and make something
of my stupid life!

19:40.079 --> 19:42.346
