have to say anything

19:42.348 --> 19:44.148
because you
already know it.

19:44.150 --> 19:45.917
I guess you're right.

19:46.352 --> 19:50.321
I also know that
if I'm gonna start college,
then you're gonna finish it.

19:50.323 --> 19:52.823
Hey, I do high-level
accounting every day.

19:52.825 --> 19:54.926
It's one credit.
Come on.

19:55.962 --> 19:57.161
Okay, fine.

19:57.163 --> 19:59.830
If you're willing
to see it through...

20:00.133 --> 20:00.798
So can I.

20:00.800 --> 20:03.701
ADULT ADAM:<i> That day,</i>
<i> my dad was the hero</i>
