20:14.247 --> 20:15.213
To the Batmobile.

20:15.215 --> 20:17.949
To the better Batmobile.

20:17.951 --> 20:20.585
ADULT ADAM:
<i> Because in the end,</i>
<i> the greatest superheroes</i>

20:20.587 --> 20:23.054
<i> ...don't have powers</i>
<i> or wear capes.</i>

20:23.056 --> 20:24.589
<i> They're the people</i>
<i> who stick with us</i>

20:24.591 --> 20:26.924
<i> through the greatest</i>
<i> adventure of all...</i>

20:26.926 --> 20:27.558
<i> Growing up.</i>

20:27.560 --> 20:30.728
<i> ¶ I bless the rains</i>
<i> down in Africa ¶</i>

20:30.730 --> 20:34.599
<i> Truth is, it's not</i>
<i> how many gadgets we have</i>
<i> in our utility belt</i>

20:34.601 --> 20:35.299
<i> that get us through life.</i>

20:35.301 --> 20:38.102
<i> What really saves the day</i>
<i> are the loved ones</i>

20:38.104 --> 20:40.504
<i> who stand by our side</i>
<i> and help us fight</i>

20:40.506 --> 20:43.107
<i> to make our dreams come true.</i>

20:56.956 --> 20:59.590
I am... Super!

