What on Earth
are you two doing?

21:17.710 --> 21:19.877
No need to be
alarmed, citizen.

21:19.879 --> 21:21.412
We are crime-fighting
professionals.

21:21.414 --> 21:24.749
Get off the side of the house,
or I'll kill both Batmans.

21:24.751 --> 21:26.751
See, that's how
you say it.

21:28.788 --> 21:31.222
I'm walking off
this picture.
